Revision history for App-GitHooks-Plugin-NotifyReleasesToSlack

v1.1.1  2016-05-21
        - Switched to Test::Requires::Git instead of the now obsolete
          Test::Git::has_git(). Thank you, Philippe Bruhat!
        - Relicensed under Perl 5 terms.

v1.1.0  2015-06-23
        - Allow notifying everyone in the release channels (GH-1).
        - Fix documentation.

v1.0.2  2015-04-20
        - Make the main line of the release more visible.
        - Don't notify the entire channel, since it does not appear to work for
          bots.


v1.0.1  2015-04-13
        - Fix post requests to Slack.
        - Improve error reporting when Slack's webhook service cannot be
          reached.

v1.0.0  2015-04-12
        - Public release.
